Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.19,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣泽车站前的【古莉】里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.39,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,有【love?dears】的初回版游戏发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.23,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,因为其中一个女主角出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.70,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,在发售日便回收了的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:31.08,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,再版后就没有了那个女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.21,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还有初回版吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:38.86,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,好...好...好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:45.52,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,神大人还是以前的神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:49.34,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让机会溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.49,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的自由被剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:55.42,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,叛逆的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:01:00.12,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来自我需跨越的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:03.45,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我所有的付出皆非徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:06.54,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,无尽欲望 难以自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.99,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,理想与现实这般痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.36,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种方法改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.97,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.33,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是重点 谁会在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:19.36,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,绘画不好 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:24.09,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,让我仅为唯一的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.82,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,克服自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:29.19,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一个只有神知道的崭新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:32.02,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:32.37,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你内心的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:36.00,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,成为骑士为你照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:35.17,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,要随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.13,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不再害怕 不再流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.81,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会迎刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:41.82,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这是“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.82,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不要误解我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.37,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:51.63,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,但我会为你做一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.46,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我的生活发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.27,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,翻过这一页来到一个新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:55.12,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 没有人可以审判我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.11,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,每个结局指向下一阶段的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.98,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,尝试让我的人生完整 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.56,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,要坚强 尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:09.81,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不要回头 继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:08.24,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,活出自己 要快乐 这是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:13.30,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为你的人生找到真爱和归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:49.34,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.49,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:55.42,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Reason as against motion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:01:00.12,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:03.45,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:06.54,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Endless desire, like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.99,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pain, the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.36,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.97,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.33,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if sing off-key, who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:19.36,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good at drawing, no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:24.09,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.82,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:29.19,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole new world god only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:32.02,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:32.37,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you’re hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:36.00,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a knight to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:35.17,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.13,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,No more fears No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.81,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:41.82,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s “god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.82,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.37,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,This in not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:51.63,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.46,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:55.12,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.27,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.11,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Every end leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.98,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to make my life complete, trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.56,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:09.81,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t look back, carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:08.24,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Be yourself be happy it's your life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:13.30,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,Find your love find your way for your life
